savedSearches.description: Oracle Fusion Apps: Business Objects Top Self-Edited Objects

uiConfig.queryString: 'Log Source' = 'Fusion Apps: HCM People Audit Logs' | extract field = 'Event Type' 'object data (?P<Action Type>.*)' | extract field = 'Business Object' 'person\s(?P<ObjectName>.*)' | extract field = Description 'null:(?P<TargetUID>\d+)\/(?P<Attr>.*):(?P<Value>.*)' | extract field = 'Qualified Business Object' 'oracle.apps.hcm.people.core.uiModel.view.manageperson(?P<VO_NAME>.*)vo' | eval isuser = contains('User Name', Description) | eval Obj_action = concat(Value, concat(_, 'Action Type')) | where isuser = 1 | stats count(ObjectName) as 'Objects Modified' by ObjectName | sort -'Objects Modified' | head

uiConfig.queryString: 'Log Source' = 'Fusion Apps: HCM People Audit Logs' | extract field = 'Event Type' 'object data (?P<Action Type>.*)' | extract field = 'Business Object' 'person\s(?P<ObjectName>.*)' | extract field = Description 'null:(?P<TargetUID>\d+)\/(?P<Attr>.*):(?P<Value>.*)' | extract field = 'Qualified Business Object' 'oracle.apps.hcm.people.core.uiModel.view.manageperson(?P<VO_NAME>.*)vo' | eval Obj_action = concat(Value, concat(_, 'Action Type')) | eval o1 = indexOf(Description, ':') | eval o2 = indexOf(Description, '/') | eval First = substr(Description, o1 + 1, o2) | eval o3 = lastIndexOf(Description, ':') | eval Second = substr(Description, o3 + 1) | where 'User Name' != Second | stats distinctcount(Second) as 'End Users', trend(distinctcount(Second))
